"replyTime":"2017-07-26T08:28:07.000Z","msg":"有種曲線宣傳套戲嘅感覺"},{"pid":"d7109652683b55364fbac4e197cf79f91864dcab","tid":335952,"uid":7371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T08:35:08.000Z","msg":"以我睇過多套路蘭戲<br />\n覺得最正都係死亡魔法<br />\n幾個好演員加好劇本加驚喜結局<br />\n就已經接近完美"},{"pid":"dac61734daa1e159d36227bd092f1c6455f2a7f8","tid":335952,"uid":48390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T08:47:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>cup連咁嘅垃圾都post出黎 睇你幾時摺<br />\n有時真係好難怪點解咁多新興網媒創立都做唔長<br />\n每次想話follow下支持下 過冇耐一定會見到呢啲垃圾文<br />\n就算少人投稿都唔代表篩選上可以放鬆啫<br />\n真係撐唔落 已unfollow</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實點垃圾法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4e8a696f1bbbe6640051e1f7891cdb7224b7a9a","tid":335952,"uid":36073,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T08:53:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>cup連咁嘅垃圾都post出黎 睇你幾時摺<br />\n有時真係好難怪點解咁多新興網媒創立都做唔長<br />\n每次想話follow下支持下 過冇耐一定會見到呢啲垃圾文<br />\n就算少人投稿都唔代表篩選上可以放鬆啫<br />\n真係撐唔落 已unfollow</blockquote><br />\n我覺得唔需要unfollow咁盡，CUP媒體本身係高質<br />\n一兩篇咪算<br />\n<br />\n呢個作者其他影評都okay<br />\n佢只係想抽HK01嗰篇影評，講晒所有佢識嘅電影，然後就話Nolan做唔到咁樣咁樣<br />\n詳情睇上面有第二條link"},{"pid":"7b649642767e59bd1f688d727cd765655170ac51","tid":335952,"uid":36073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T09:09:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有種曲線宣傳套戲嘅感覺</blockquote><br />\n學你個名，其實係直線宣傳<br />\n作者本身就係覺得套戲好睇<br />\n冇需要因為Nolan做唔到以前經典電影嘅效果，而踩套戲<br />\n<br />\nDunkirk本身我覺得係以描寫事實為主題，3線連貫拍出歷史<br />\n再加啲電影嘅元素，例如探討人性、勝利同失敗<br />\n佢想造出另類戰爭電影，或者Nolan叫做Suspense thriller<br />\n<br />\n我覺得Dunkirk係另類手法看戰爭，甚至好少戰爭元素，<br />\n著重戰場上嘅人性討論，去讚揚當時為咗大撤退而付出嘅所有人。<br />\n套戲手法其實算係獨特，至少我對每個畫面都有深刻印象。"},{"pid":"ec971994a135a814602702c0f7bfe565dcae2382","tid":335952,"uid":41477,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:23:32.000Z","msg":"睇番倫敦首映，問番當年係現場既老兵套戲拍成點，佢地話拍得好真實，咁就夠啦。"},{"pid":"3facf8dba39e75d3ce0a1f80bd2467653821c124","tid":335952,"uid":27616,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:33:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇番倫敦首映，問番當年係現場既老兵套戲拍成點，佢地話拍得好真實，咁就夠啦。</blockquote><br />\n連登仔:d廢老收左錢先咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adf58f524a199a053a4a84d3d7828cbbedcfa64d","tid":335952,"uid":24593,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:33:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇番倫敦首映，問番當年係現場既老兵套戲拍成點，佢地話拍得好真實，咁就夠啦。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n連登仔話英國老兵算什麼？<br />\n明明套野話四十萬人大撒退 我見到個沙灘最多得千幾人<br />\n完全唔寫實 冇做好資料搜集<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0200c904b535918d174ec3b89c036b6f198481d","tid":335952,"uid":41343,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:35:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港人真係on9，以屌Marvel 獨孤一味唔認真為例，但人地片尾要列成十分鐘cast and production</blockquote><br />\n有咩關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />變形金剛盜墓迷城咁垃圾片尾credit都係咁長架啦<br />\n美國片慣例要列哂所有工作人員出黎"},{"pid":"526fadbe1a93c2de0bbabef3c29643cd6363c3c4","tid":335952,"uid":27616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:37:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇番倫敦首映，問番當年係現場既老兵套戲拍成點，佢地話拍得好真實，咁就夠啦。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n連登仔話英國老兵算什麼？<br />\n明明套野話四十萬人大撒退 我見到個沙灘最多得千幾人<br />\n完全唔寫實 冇做好資料搜集<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n沙灘太乾淨，屍體排得太整齊，整亂佢都懶，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd5dd4b47a67e5916d595be45a38d90087c6ef4a","tid":335952,"uid":92600,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:50:48.000Z","msg":"其實寫得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想知有咩問題<br />\n<br />\n又口語又書面語係早幾十年嘅寫法<br />\n有時仲會加埋文言文 叫三及第<br />\n<br />\n其實陶傑同李碧華都係單單打打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾百字好難論述啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n英文專欄有時都會用呢種反諷寫法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2175a0dced6f2d025fa63d5b100b012b382d039","tid":335952,"uid":4349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T10:58:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>成篇野文筆單單打打成個八婆咁<br />\n得罪講句，即使佢d論點論據係啱，我都唔覺篇野幾有說服力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n難道你還不知道嗎，在歷史上的電影大師面前，大家都是零。自從寇比力克、史匹堡、列尼史葛拍過電影以後，其他電影就不配再出現在這個世界上了。以後有人要拍太空片嗎，先把「2001 太空漫遊」搬出來吧；有人要拍外星人片嗎，問過 ET 和「第三類接觸」沒有？還是你要拍未來科幻片嘛，難道你會覺得自己拍得比 Blade Runner 好看嗎？<span style=\"color: red;\">望咩啊望，講緊你啊路蘭，眼高手低啊你，唔夠史詩啊，學乜嘢人用配樂啫，係無信心嘅表現嚟架，返去好好反省吓啦。</span></blockquote><br />\n請問大師可以點改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a855ad0c7c6a80ce21c874a5dbc1a7bf0dea7532","tid":335952,"uid":36073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T11:32:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇番倫敦首映，問番當年係現場既老兵套戲拍成點，佢地話拍得好真實，咁就夠啦。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n連登仔話英國老兵算什麼？<br />\n明明套野話四十萬人大撒退 我見到個沙灘最多得千幾人<br />\n完全唔寫實 冇做好資料搜集<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n沙灘太乾淨，屍體排得太整齊，整亂佢都懶，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲要拍攝嗰時請得幾百個臨記<br />\n其他就用紙板人，紙板車<br />\n咁hea 當人傻架，成億美金預算去晒邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57056f61e9e51cb3a0aacd7d7bcfad4663dc3b57","tid":335952,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T12:22:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個作者咩心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n終於開始多人知道nolan過譽, 留意到<span style=\"color: red;\">imax濫用配樂</span>既問題, 佢就一盤冷水淋埋去, 話人扮專家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 配樂關imax咩事？"},{"pid":"16d242a526b6234910861766f2d2dbb40bb0e636","tid":335952,"uid":10626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T12:27:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>曲線曲得咁唔好笑嘅文都係第一次見</blockquote><br />\n呢個真"},{"pid":"7a875d3e662ce822fd0a03ab9eb76a077a6ff67f","tid":335952,"uid":37885,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T01:17:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實寫得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想知有咩問題<br />\n<br />\n又口語又書面語係早幾十年嘅寫法<br />\n有時仲會加埋文言文 叫三及第<br />\n<br />\n其實陶傑同李碧華都係單單打打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾百字好難論述啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">英文專欄有時都會用呢種反諷寫法</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係話佢用反諷有問題, 但出到嚟嘅效果係似小學雞同潑婦罵街, 同19嗰啲抽水差幾十皮<br />\n<br />\n同埋我唔清楚你紅字嗰句想表達啲乜?"},{"pid":"c05637602eb45cf525f93270b5240af64ee66ebd","tid":335952,"uid":48631,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T04:34:25.000Z","msg":"篇文小學雞到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8009cf366a3bb22497805d972204b128c887628","tid":335952,"uid":34186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T04:43:33.000Z","msg":"似連登仔比人屌講中條氣唔順多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />鳩up 幾句扮電影大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c31484af9ddf3b44b61143f6d36c980c754aa234","tid":335952,"uid":55192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T08:01:49.000Z","msg":"其實不嬲睇戲 都係要先睇啲觀眾評價<br />\n一般正負評反差大嘅 <br />\n即係有好多人話悶、唔好睇<br />\n但又有好多人讚<br />\n通常都好值得入場睇 <br />\n<br />\n估唔到有人而家直線（其實只係唔開名 都唔曲喇）抽擊影評 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n此風可長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：未睇套戲 但有好大期望"},{"pid":"3fce144a681cfd6015796333aceaccb487ff2e55","tid":335952,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T08:22:10.000Z","msg":"屌你 拍電影前唔資料搜集 拍完出來比人捉到錯處比人屌有咩問題？<br />\n<br />\n個作者鐘意睇蝗國 抗日神劇？<br />\n8年抗戰開始了？"},{"pid":"6ba99ef3120b734046407920ae0724456ac184a8","tid":335952,"uid":48733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T08:27:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c2d6159614d958add313eee2df35d9fb8319635","tid":335952,"uid":116896,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T08:38:42.000Z","msg":"講真<br />\n呢套戲近10年top 3戰爭片啦，無得拗<br />\n都唔明d人做咩為反而反<br />\n香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0cfbf4b5200f9c914905161ed3c710c8c2fc79a","tid":335952,"uid":48479,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T08:42:39.000Z","msg":"呢d抽水論調根本毫無意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地批評套戲就譏諷人地係&ldquo;全世界最懂電影的人&rdquo;，咁讚套戲又使唔使係&ldquo;全世界最懂電影的人&rdquo;先可以讚？<br />\n無論正反，終歸都係講理據同論點，如果你唔同意某篇影評嘅意見，請寫返篇文章逐一指正 (好似之前朗天同譚以諾就《下女誘罪》嘅筆戰)，而唔係寫埋d毫無意義嘅抽水文，咁只顯得自己八婆兼小家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ed88d1550949a89f4617b2e678f81bd7b48b7cc","tid":335952,"uid":35637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T08:48:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你 拍電影前唔資料搜集 拍完出來比人捉到錯處比人屌有咩問題？<br />\n<br />\n個作者鐘意睇蝗國 抗日神劇？<br />\n8年抗戰開始了？</blockquote><br />\n問題係套戲其實冇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n歷史上個沙灘真係咁乾淨<br />\n真係冇任何軍備<br />\n真係一批一批咁走<br />\n所以每次幾千人合理<br />\n係班觀眾覺得同預期戰爭片唔同先9屌"},{"pid":"92c2720e321bfdab6250950aa842831e518ae536","tid":335952,"uid":36167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T08:49:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你 拍電影前唔資料搜集 拍完出來比人捉到錯處比人屌有咩問題？<br />\n<br />\n個作者鐘意睇蝗國 抗日神劇？<br />\n8年抗戰開始了？</blockquote><br />\n人地二戰舊兵睇完表示好似身歷其境咁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dd67b360458669749ba84e041da033de4d5508a","tid":335952,"uid":48479,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T08:50:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講真<br />\n呢套戲近10年top 3戰爭片啦，無得拗<br />\n都唔明d人做咩為反而反<br />\n香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又話唔係戰爭片嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無論點，你Dunkirk係近10年top 3戰爭片我無咩異議，畢竟呢10年好嘅戰爭片唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但亦無必要一面倒唱好，有不足嘅地方都應該要講出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實一隻手掌拍唔響，一班人踩得咁勁係因為另一班人捧得太勁，反之亦然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d51b6db1c2ea2e74eff6770f7918698ba109fa4","tid":335952,"uid":35637,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T08:51:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌你 拍電影前唔資料搜集 拍完出來比人捉到錯處比人屌有咩問題？<br />\n<br />\n個作者鐘意睇蝗國 抗日神劇？<br />\n8年抗戰開始了？</blockquote><br />\n人地二戰舊兵睇完表示好似身歷其境咁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n班觀眾想睇史詩式戰爭場面<br />\n但呢個其實係走佬大行動黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係拍到血肉橫飛先on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"013b20c0dd8bb3002e5380210bfb22f0f9ae43b7","tid":335952,"uid":116896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T09:00:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講真<br />\n呢套戲近10年top 3戰爭片啦，無得拗<br />\n都唔明d人做咩為反而反<br />\n香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又話唔係戰爭片嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無論點，你Dunkirk係近10年top 3戰爭片我無咩異議，畢竟呢10年好嘅戰爭片唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但亦無必要一面倒唱好，有不足嘅地方都應該要講出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實一隻手掌拍唔響，一班人踩得咁勁係因為另一班人捧得太勁，反之亦然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好野驚咩人踩<br />\n當年黑夜之神岩岩上俾人踩英雄片唔應該咁<br />\n到今日，邊個仲踩緊？<br />\n路遙知馬力😎"},{"pid":"35d9956fbe2decbafd370fbd907b13dd15638968","tid":335952,"uid":36167,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T09:00:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講真<br />\n呢套戲近10年top 3戰爭片啦，無得拗<br />\n都唔明d人做咩為反而反<br />\n香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又話唔係戰爭片嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無論點，你Dunkirk係近10年top 3戰爭片我無咩異議，畢竟呢10年好嘅戰爭片唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但亦無必要一面倒唱好，有不足嘅地方都應該要講出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實一隻手掌拍唔響，一班人踩得咁勁係因為另一班人捧得太勁，反之亦然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n總括而言呢套係一套有缺點嘅好片<br />\n無可否認有啲人平時戲都唔睇多套<br />\n見到Nolan個名就捧定先扮識戲<br />\n但連登有班人就係鐘意見紅就踩<br />\n見Nolan多人捧